{"tid":478270,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以係大公司入面做到冇存在感？","createTime":"2017-11-24T02:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T04:36:56.000Z","uid":68728,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"da95aa6931b3df72e35cbb712fc8ea141be31761","tid":478270,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"細公司冇可能啦<br />\n<br />\n大公司一層有超過一百人 一個上司可能要睇十個細 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以做到上司唔太記得你既存在 可能一個月先搵你幾次 只係比啲濕鳩野你做 而你每日就好得閒 扮工 唔張揚咁玩 <br />\n<br />\n最正係栽員時 只係記得最差個啲員工 根本諗到冇諗過你 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打成功做到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cb481ad47fbe82ca203d75751e9c243dc84e7c","tid":478270,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9fa4a77eaf416699e1451de715f528243a8dc2","tid":478270,"uid":102096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44a8da7c31b4bcab6f6c33f3da7d850466fcb096","tid":478270,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"55e91de2669cd1ce57db6704d49f2b8db3759ba9","tid":478270,"uid":68728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要就係平時唔出聲, 唔同其他同事做非必要交流<br />\n慢慢大家就會唔覺你存在<br />\n當然位置好緊要<br />\n我坐緊全公司最角果個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔係成日都好HEA？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a605a1818b459c96b29c780edcefcc155b57cc7","tid":478270,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80bed3f2403e7784ffae3dda8ea4c00b19cf7cf","tid":478270,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:16:00.